SHARM EL SHEIKH, Egypt, March 27, 2018/APO Group/ -- 
                                                
                        The World Tourism Organization (UNWTO) in conjunction with the Minister of Tourism of the Arab Republic of Egypt, has the pleasure to invite Arab Members to the celebration of the statutory meeting of the 44th UNWTO Commission for the Middle East, to be held on 08 May 2018, in Sharm el Sheikh, Arab Republic of Egypt. The Commission meeting will be followed by the UNWTO Regional Conference on Tourism Human Capital Development: New Perspectives, to be held on 9 May 2018.